1
00:00:00,230 --> 00:00:02,830
我们被称为密特拉之子
We are known as the Sons of Mithras.

2
00:00:03,230 --> 00:00:06,830
鬼火 这就是密特拉神之子的杰作
Ignis fatuus, that's what this Sons of Mithras business is.

3
00:00:06,960 --> 00:00:08,730
如果我娶了卡米拉・帕吉...
If I marry Camilla Pazzi...

4
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:11,960
你我仍然可以不时地偷欢
You and I can still snatch a little freedom here and there.

5
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:14,060
要在洛伦佐过来的路上动手吗?
Do we kill Lorenzo coming up the path?

6
00:00:14,260 --> 00:00:15,560
只有他们兄弟两个在一起的时候 我们才能动手
Strike only when the brothers are together.

7
00:00:15,700 --> 00:00:17,000
卢克蕾齐娅・多纳蒂?
Lucrezia Donati?

8
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:19,530
备马去锡耶纳 我们当面问她
Saddle the horses for Siena. We'll question her directly.

9
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:22,230
- 这位就是最后一位救世主  - 先生们
- And here's our final savior.  - Gentlemen.

10
00:00:22,530 --> 00:00:25,360
是什么让你背叛洛伦佐 背叛我们大家?
What possesses you to betray Lorenzo, to betray us all?

11
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:30,300
- 你是卢克蕾齐娅・多纳蒂的父亲  - 是的
- You are Lucrezia Donati's father.  - Indeed.

12
00:00:33,260 --> 00:00:35,830
艺术家 我看到你逃出来了
L'Artista, I see you escaped.

13
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:37,100
而我看到了一把钥匙
And I see a key.

14
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,630
科西莫・美第奇是密特拉之子
Cosimo de Medici was a Son of Mithras.

15
00:00:40,860 --> 00:00:43,160
一艘装了探险补给的船
A ship provisioned for a journey.

16
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:45,560
天穹就在那
The Vault of Heaven is out there.

