speaking of... other times and other lives.

512
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:16,030
或许... 如果他们所说是真的...
Maybe... if they're correct...

513
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:21,500
有另一个世界存在于我们...
a life exists in which we...

