A ship waits in Pisa to take me to the Book of Leaves.

520
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,460
要是我没有登上王冠蜥蜴号...
If I'm not on the Basilisk...

521
00:38:43,700 --> 00:38:46,200
瑞阿里奥和帕吉的军队已经逼近佛罗伦萨
Riario and the Pazzis are moving on Florence.

522
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:50,700
