523
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:54,330
让政客们互相残杀吧 那是他们的专长
Let the politicians kill each other, that's their forte.

524
00:38:54,530 --> 00:38:58,230
莱昂纳多 求求你 如今只有你能阻止这一切
Leonardo, please, you are only one who can stop this now.

525
00:38:59,560 --> 00:39:02,060
