有件事我必须去做
There's something I must do.

616
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:35,730
- 没时间了  - 驳船不会等你的 你想清楚了
- There's no time.  - The barge won't wait. Make a decision.

617
00:47:36,030 --> 00:47:38,800
叶之书还是女人 不可兼得啊
The Book Of Leaves or whoever tears you away. You can't have both.

618
00:47:39,060 --> 00:47:43,730
我可以 我可以的 只要你们能想办法让船等我回来
I can. I can, if you just find a way to keep them here until I return.

619
00:47:44,000 --> 00:47:46,800
我很快就回来 想想办法 琐罗
I'm not gonna be long. Just stall them, Zo.

620
00:47:46,930 --> 00:47:48,060
求你了!
Please!

621
00:47:52,630 --> 00:47:54,500
这就是那张牌的另一个意思
There's another meaning to that card.

622
00:47:54,660 --> 00:47:56,400
被阻挡的旅途
A journey thwarted.

623
00:47:57,730 --> 00:48:02,760
以圣父 圣子 圣灵之名
In nominee Patris, et Filii, et Spiritus Sancti.

624
