聪明的人... 对上帝应怀爱与惧之心
The wise... both fear and love God.

627
00:48:18,500 --> 00:48:21,600
那你为什么犹豫不敢进入他的圣殿?
Why then do you hesitate to enter His house?

628
00:48:21,800 --> 00:48:24,760
因为在门后等着我的并不是上帝
Because it isn't God who waits for me inside those doors.

629
00:48:24,960 --> 00:48:28,330
聆听子民的祈祷 赐予他们想要的圣体
tui, cum oblationibus hostiarum:

630
00:48:28,360 --> 00:48:31,900
如你在逾越节所作的
ut paschalibus initiata mysteriis,

631
00:48:32,160 --> 00:48:35,200
您的赠与 
ad aeternitatis  nobis medelam,

632
00:48:35,360 --> 00:48:37,830
