635
00:48:43,700 --> 00:48:46,060
两匹
Two.

636
00:48:50,560 --> 00:48:52,360
厄运将降临在这座城市
Hell is descending upon this city.

637
00:48:52,560 --> 00:48:55,360
快 找个安全地方躲起来
Get yourself to safety. Now.

638
00:49:57,300 --> 00:49:58,730
