哥哥! 哥哥! 帮帮你的亲人!
Brother! Brother! Help your family!

656
00:51:35,260 --> 00:51:37,900
罗马才是我的亲人
Rome is my family.

657
00:51:38,060 --> 00:51:39,730
请原谅
Forgive me.

658
00:51:41,760 --> 00:51:44,830
- 啊!  - 朱利亚诺!
- Aaargh!  - Giuliano!

659
00:51:47,630 --> 00:51:50,560
