00:53:21,800 --> 00:53:26,230
如果你真的忠诚于美第奇家 队长...
If your true loyalty is to the Medicis, Captain... 

679
00:53:26,500 --> 00:53:30,160
我建议你带他们走 这个留给我
I suggest you take them away and leave this one to me.

680
00:53:30,360 --> 00:53:33,460
- 但多纳蒂夫人...  - 已经背叛你们投靠罗马了
- But Signora Donati...  - Has betrayed you for Rome.

681
00:53:33,660 --> 00:53:36,860
让他们狗咬狗去吧 夫人
Leave them to each other, Signora.

682
00:53:37,030 --> 00:53:40,130
孩子们
Children.

683
00:53:40,300 --> 00:53:42,360
快走
Hurry.

684
00:53:44,160 --> 00:53:46,700
不...
No... 

685
00:53:50,160 --> 00:53:52,730
我一直祈祷这一天的来临 今天 佛罗伦萨欢欣鼓舞
I've prayed for this day. Today, Florence rejoices.

686
00:53:52,860 --> 00:53:54,660
你真以为会那样吗? 帕吉?
Are you certain of that, Pazzi?

687
00:54:06,400 --> 00:54:07,400
啊!
Aaargh!

688
00:54:12,830 --> 00:54:14,130
洛伦佐 临死之前
Before you die, Lorenzo,

689
00:54:14,360 --> 00:54:16,600
让你知道 我将会杀尽佛罗伦萨所有美第奇家的人
know that I'll kill every last Medici in Florence.

690
00:54:16,930 --> 00:54:20,860
我要将你家族的痕迹从世界上完全抹除!
I'll wipe all evidence of your family's existence from this world!

691
00:54:23,860 --> 00:54:25,560
剑不用会生锈
Iron rusts from disuse.

692
00:54:41,160 --> 00:54:43,860
让我们消灭美第奇家族 小作家
Let us finish off the Medicis, scribbler,

693
00:54:43,900 --> 00:54:45,530
你还可以苟活
and we might let you live.

694
00:54:45,660 --> 00:54:49,060
帕吉家族掌管佛罗伦萨? 绝不!
A Florence ruled by Pazzis? No!

695
00:54:49,330 --> 00:54:52,360
我更愿意为此而战
No. I think I'd rather go down fighting.

696
00:54:52,530 --> 00:54:53,660
遂你所愿
As you wish.

697
00:55:04,360 --> 00:55:07,030
快点 快点!
Come on. Come on!

698
00:55:08,630 --> 00:55:11,730
快点! 快点!
Come on! Come on!

699
00:55:20,130 --> 00:55:23,060
- 那撑不了多久的  - 门能撑住
- That won't hold long.  - The doors will hold.

700
00:55:23,300 --> 00:55:26,730
韦罗基奥设计的锁具
Verrocchio designed the locks.

701
00:55:30,260 --> 00:55:34,130
朱利亚诺呢? 我弟弟死了吗?
Giuliano? Have I lost a brother?

702
00:55:37,230 --> 00:55:40,360
给我砸! 砸开 砸开!
Come on! Come on, come on!

703
00:55:41,360 --> 00:55:42,700
达芬奇!
Da Vinci!

704
00:55:42,860 --> 00:55:45,330
我来的时候只看到你
Upon my arrival I saw only you.

705
00:55:48,930 --> 00:55:52,400
- 我知道你不会不管我们的  - 别说了 省点劲吧
- I knew you wouldn't abandon us.  - Stop. Save your strength.

706
00:55:53,560 --> 00:55:55,460
达芬奇!
Da Vinci!

707
00:56:00,360 --> 00:56:02,100
很快就有结果啦 卢克蕾齐娅!
It'll be over soon, Lucrezia!

708
00:56:05,760 --> 00:56:10,060
很抱歉 莱昂纳多 你救了我 我知道这对你来说...
I'm sorry, Leonardo. You've saved my life, and I know what it's cost y... 

709
00:56:10,300 --> 00:56:13,930
嘘 把你的赞美之词留给值得的人吧
Ssh. Save your praise for someone who deserves it.

710
00:56:14,230 --> 00:56:17,200
你希望他们中的哪一个为你陪葬?
I wonder which of the two men you fuck will be buried alongside you?

711
00:56:17,430 --> 00:56:20,260
你放弃梦想 选择了保卫佛罗伦萨
You chose Florence over your own dreams.

712
00:56:20,400 --> 00:56:22,260
请接受我的敬意
You will accept my love.

713
00:56:22,460 --> 00:56:24,530
我也只能向你致敬了
It is the least I can offer you.

714
00:56:27,230 --> 00:56:31,600
这戒指 我认识这戒指
This ring. I know this ring.

715
00:56:34,760 --> 00:56:37,100
这是卢克蕾齐娅的
It's Lucrezia's.

716
00:56:41,530 --> 00:56:45,860
你跟她上床了... 或者更甚?
Are you fucking her... or is it more?

717
00:56:48,700 --> 00:56:51,630
要么你现在帮他们干掉我 否则我发誓...
You better finish the job they have begun or I swear... 

718
00:56:51,900 --> 00:56:55,430
如果我们能生还 我要把你俩都杀掉
if we survive this, I'll kill you both.

719
00:56:57,460 --> 00:57:00,760
领受上帝的复仇之怒吧!
God's vengeance is upon you!

